---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pinehurst Golf Trips — Plan Your Sandhills Golf Getaway"
  description="The independent, opinionated guide to planning a golf trip to Pinehurst, Southern Pines, and the Sandhills of North Carolina. Course reviews, itinerary tips, dining, and lodging."
>
  {/* Hero */}
  <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center">
    <img
      src="/images/hero.jpg"
      alt="View of a Pinehurst golf course fairway through longleaf pines"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/35"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28 w-full">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold italic text-white max-w-3xl">
        Plan Your Pinehurst Area Golf&nbsp;Trip
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        An honest, independent guide to golf in the Sandhills of North Carolina &mdash;
        covering Pinehurst, Southern Pines, Aberdeen, and the courses that make this
        one of the best golf destinations on the East Coast.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="/courses"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-dark-green font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors"
        >
          Browse Courses
        </a>
        <a
          href="/guide"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-dark-green transition-colors"
        >
          First-Timer's Guide
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Intro */}
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-olive font-bold">
      What you won't find here
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      This isn't the resort's marketing site, and it's not a booking engine. It's the guide
      I wish existed when I was planning my first Pinehurst trip &mdash; price tiers, honest course
      rankings, and practical advice from someone who's actually walked (some of) the fairways.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I'll help you figure out which courses are worth the greens fee, which ones you can skip, and what
      to do with the hours between rounds. If I haven't played a course myself, I'll say so
      and tell you what the consensus says instead.
    </p>
  </section>

  {/* Section cards */}
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pb-16 md:pb-24">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {/* Courses */}
      <a href="/courses" class="group block no-underline bg-dark-green p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-dark-green/90 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white font-bold font-heading">
          Course Guide
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-cream/70 leading-relaxed">
          20+ courses organized by tier &mdash; from the championship stage of No.&nbsp;2 to local
          favorites worth the detour. Honest takes, real prices.
        </p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-cream/70 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
          View all courses &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>

      {/* Guide */}
      <a href="/guide" class="group block no-underline bg-dark-green p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-dark-green/90 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white font-bold font-heading">
          First-Timer's Guide
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-cream/70 leading-relaxed">
          Everything you need for your first trip &mdash; when to go, how to book, caddie tips,
          packing, and the FAQ everyone asks.
        </p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-cream/70 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
          Read the guide &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>

      {/* Contact */}
      <a href="/contact" class="group block no-underline bg-dark-green p-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-dark-green/90 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white font-bold font-heading">
          Ask a Question
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-cream/70 leading-relaxed">
          Planning a trip and not sure where to start? Drop a question and I'll
          help you figure out courses, timing, budget &mdash; whatever you need.
        </p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-cream/70 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
          Get in touch &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
